title: Johnny Staccato (1959) 1-22 directed by John Cassavets
description:
Johnny Staccato (1959) Episode Twenty Two:"Solomon" Directed by John Cassavetes

featuring Cloris Leachman and Elisha Cook Jr.

runtime 26 min.

Introducing this series to torrents in a small file size. There is a wiki for this series with many details. In these fileshares I will not repeat a lot of that.

From the wiki

Johnny Staccato is an American private detective series starring John Cassavetes which ran for 27 episodes on NBC from September 10, 1959 through March 24, 1960.

1-22 	"Solomon" 	February 11, 1960 	A pacifist movement leader (Cloris Leachman) is accused of murdering her husband, which results in the woman's lawyer (Elisha Cook, Jr.) coming to Staccato for help.

  [ This is a standout episode.  Cloris Leachman is hard to recognize as her younger self but the quality of the performance is not difficult to recognise at all.]
